Package app

Class Photos

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • app.Photos
  • public class Photos
extends javafx.application.Application
    The Photos class is the main application driver for the project. It contains the main method that launches the project as an application. Photos is serializable and contains the logic that is used within the entire application such as saving data, loading data, getting logged in user etc.
    Author:
    Vincent Phung, William McFarland
